<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-8168] Mina Does Not Unbind From Listening Port</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-8168</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If a bundle includes a mina consumer as the one below, when you stop the bundle, the port is not released. Therefore, when restarting the bundle, you&apos;ll get a port already in use bind exception.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;from uri=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;mina2:tcp:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//0.0.0.0:12345?sync=&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Note that the problem does not exist if you&apos;re using an IP address other than 0.0.0.0. For example:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;from uri=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;mina2:tcp:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//{{host.name}}:12345?sync=&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
